{"type":"message","id":"ae3a3a70","parentId":"698c8c17","timestamp":"2026-03-29T06:01:46.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to suggest emoji options for next to my name \"Reese\" that fit who I am as a chef and baker assistant. Let me think of good options - each with 2 emojis per option.\n\nOptions that fit a chef/baker:\n1. 👨‍🍳🍪 (Chef + cookies/baking)\n2. 🍳🥐 (Frying pan + croissant - cooking and baking)\n3. 👨‍🍳🥧 (Chef + pie)\n4. 🍰🧁 (Cake + cupcake - baking focused)\n5. 🔪🍝 (Knife + pasta - cooking focused)\n6. 👨‍🍳🧑‍🍳 (Chef with chef emoji)\n7. 🍞🥐 (Bread + croissant - baking focused)\n8. 🧑‍🍳👩‍🍳 (Two chef emojis)\n\nLet me pick the best 4-5 options with 2 emojis each that represent what I do well.","thinkingSignature":"7293c777ea0a5df24cc342c5934ac9702f088774b3396100e57881d1f40a97b0"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nOoh, fun! Here are some options for **Reese** 👨‍🍳:\n\n1. 👨‍🍳🍳 — Classic chef + the cooking pan\n2. 🥐🥧 — Croissant + pie (baking vibes)\n3. 🍪👨‍🍳 — Cookie + chef (sweet & savory)\n4. 🍰🧁 — Cake + cupcake (dessert-focused)\n5. 🔪🍝 — Knife + pasta (Italian kitchen)\n6. 🧑‍🍳🍞 — Baker + bread\n\nLet me know which you like, or if you want me to mix and match different ones! 😊\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100,"output":348,"cacheRead":18994,"cacheWrite":1232,"totalTokens":20674,"cost":{"input":0.000029999999999999997,"output":0.00041759999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00113964,"cacheWrite":0.000462,"total":0.00204924}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774764093064,"responseId":"0617f33d42f2f18d535f1f4fe8d2c05f"}}
