ch\\n---\\nr/Cooking on Reddit: Trying to recreate Asian zing\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea6c80540a98950b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.reddit.com/r/Cooking/comments/jecd86/trying_to_recreate_asian_zing/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"18a5e4ec558891f1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTrying to make the Asian zing wing sauce from BWW and I think I have an idea on what to do but looking for recommendations. Was going to crush a star anise pods in a mortal and pestle into a dust, take that out then crush a few cloves of garlic and chilis into a paste.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"18a5e4ec558891f1\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"October 19, 2020\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.reddit.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"best asian zing sauce copycat recipe highest rated reviews","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":717,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ad0f58b222ad1eea\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAsian Zing Sauce Recipe (Great for Chicken Wings) - Spoons Of Flavor\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ad0f58b222ad1eea\">>>","url":"https://spoonsofflavor.com/asian-zing-sauce/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6f81e2b69eceb5db\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThis is a copycat recipe of <strong>Buffalo Wild Wings Asian Zing Sauce</strong>. This sweet and spicy blend of chili pepper, soy, and ginger is perfect for wings, but it&#x27;s also great on various other dishes like chicken tenders, meatballs, shrimp, and vegetables ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6f81e2b69eceb5db\">>>","published":"September 2, 2025","siteName":"spoonsofflavor.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2f3c3ecdee235f76\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAsian Zing Sauce - My Sweet Precision\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2f3c3ecdee235f76\">>>","ur