{"type":"message","id":"9a1aced8","parentId":"12c017df","timestamp":"2026-03-30T02:02:59.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby says he'll try it first. I should respond encouragingly and offer to help if he needs anything!","thinkingSignature":"bc3b0db03367b99c19ccb705b1d6062286d9d5e12675e13ca265cb9dcd99e06b"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nThat's the spirit! 🙌 \n\nLet me know how it turns out — and if you tweak anything to make it even more BWW-like, I'd love to hear about it so we can perfect YOUR version of the recipe. 🍪👨‍🍳\n\nIf you need help with anything — like suggested wing cooking times, sides, or even scaling up the recipe for a crowd — just ask! Good luck and enjoy! 🍗✨\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86,"output":120,"cacheRead":29474,"cacheWrite":6529,"totalTokens":36209,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774836172536,"responseId":"06190ccd898dc4cdada2829bff812654"}}
